des: "A delicious and refreshing snack for any time of day. An indulgence that's healthy and tastes great. Add more or less sugar based on what your taste is."
ins: Blend raspberries in a blender until pureed; pour raspberries through a sieve to strain seeds. Discard seeds. Blend seedless-raspberry puree, yogurt, sugar, and cottage cheese in a blender until smooth; pour mixture into ice pop molds or paper cups. Insert ice pop sticks into mixture and freeze until solid, at least 4 hours.
